name: David Sheldon
what_you_do: Day.you is a comprehensive guide that explores the meanings and origins of the days of the week and common holidays, providing insights into their historical and cultural significance.
who_you_serve: The website serves individuals interested in learning about the calendar, including students, educators, and anyone curious about the origins of days and holidays.
